{"tid":411663,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人由細到大做乜撚嘢都半途而廢？","createTime":"2017-09-24T04:32:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-24T07:39:54.000Z","uid":60015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0de47046b1ec089fad3851dfddf13655e77ed121","tid":411663,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:32:19.000Z","msg":"我真係好撚垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由細到大都冇樣嘢學得成同做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個老母叫我學鋼琴<br />\n學咗一排又荒廢<br />\n學過小提琴<br />\n今次學過幾年<br />\n但學嚟學去都考唔到級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後開始學下日文<br />\n上兩堂又開始唔返<br />\n到大個又再重新學過<br />\n諗住好有決心<br />\n點知學到n4又開始唔學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n細個讀書唔洗講<br />\n都係廢嗰啲<br />\n我覺得我呢啲性格令我成為真正人生失敗者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6158c952a2e79711f18446d6773687931d32ac7","tid":411663,"uid":7475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c429cd178a7b304753a4edc063ea375ca22dc2f","tid":411663,"uid":2419,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:33:39.000Z","msg":"起碼你打得晒呢篇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf0bec74d1c0434266fa914f9d6736c0b671017","tid":411663,"uid":57058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T04:36:27.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日試新野玩，但無樣玩得耐/專<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n周身刀無張利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6e0033a0d9081a0c082bae94d8a22df96c3006b","tid":411663,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:09:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>起碼你打得晒呢篇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打到一半有諗過唔打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過見返工好得閒咪打埋佢"},{"pid":"f6d170383b60c4cc426d9e341183fc75ec20a7b8","tid":411663,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:10:50.000Z","msg":"我又試過減肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但跑2日步就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d994db9d32eb87ad76fd51cd5e23885e2b266779","tid":411663,"uid":60015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:11:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日試新野玩，但無樣玩得耐/專<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n周身刀無張利<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/15.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但你肯試新嘢<br />\n我唔撚肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d89c88f65a204f8297c8da789cb37b87ba2eac1","tid":411663,"uid":68944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T07:39:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n見啲嘢難/麻煩果陣就唔想去做"}]}